1020
01:22:43.260 --> 01:22:43.740
No.

1021
01:22:44.220 --> 01:22:45.220
Adam.

1022
01:22:45.660 --> 01:22:46.660
Adam. this is a trap.

1023
01:22:47.380 --> 01:22:49.276
