1040
01:23:24.360 --> 01:23:25.360
Adam.

1041
01:23:27.450 --> 01:23:28.450
We are with you.

1042
01:23:33.180 --> 01:23:34.180
At every turn.

1043
01:23:36.140 --> 01:23:38.510
