1058
01:25:11.210 --> 01:25:12.310
Hold the sword.

1059
01:25:13.190 --> 01:25:14.190
Guard!

1060
01:25:24.440 --> 01:25:30.700
Take this one and his lovely muscles to
Lord Skeletor.

1061
01:25:32.050 --> 01:25:33.480
