1072
01:26:54.530 --> 01:26:57.130
Now give me the sword.

1073
01:26:59.390 --> 01:27:00.630
Let it go.

1074
01:27:01.610 --> 01:27:02.610
Hmm.

1075
01:27:03.070 --> 01:27:04.250
I said it first.

1076
01:27:04.830 --> 01:27:05.830
Let it go!

1077
01:27:06.230 --> 01:27:09.430
