1096
01:31:35.810 --> 01:31:36.810
Oh. yeah.

1097
01:32:15.330 --> 01:32:16.330
Adam?

1098
01:32:18.520 --> 01:32:19.630
To see you.

1099
01:32:22.960 --> 01:32:24.270
