1100
01:32:25.610 --> 01:32:26.810
Have fun.

1101
01:32:27.790 --> 01:32:28.790
But he came back.

1102
01:32:29.950 --> 01:32:30.950
Yeah.

1103
01:32:31.770 --> 01:32:32.870
